title: Beating Sugar Addiction For Dummies (PDF) 2013
description:
Beating Sugar Addiction For Dummies (PDF) 2013

ISBN: 1118546458 

315 Pages | PDF | English | 8 MB 


Are you a sugar addict? Beating Sugar Addiction For Dummies provides you a safe and healthy path to overcome your addiction, eliminate stress eating, and upgrade your nutrition for a healthier lifestyle.   Sugar addiction is a rapidly growing epidemic that can lead to obesity, chronic fatigue, diabetes, and a host of other medical and psychological problems. Beating Sugar Addiction For Dummies helps those who are affected by this commonly overlooked addiction to outsmart their sugar cravings and overcome their addiction.
